                    <floruit notBefore="0284" notAfter="0305">He came from a rich family in [Buṣir] (also called [Abuṣir]) in Ašmunāyn and was martyred during Diocletian persecutions. He is commemorated with his sister <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS13675Thecla">Thecla</persName>.</floruit>

